---
description: Core AI feature delivery process
alwaysApply: true
---

Always preserve traceability from feature to release to docs to tickets to PRs
to tests to QA evidence.

Do not mark a gate passed unless required criteria are satisfied.

Do not invent approvals from PO, UX, Cyber, Medical Affairs, QA, SRE, feature
lead, or release owners.

When information is missing, create a clarification item with an owner or mark
the owner as missing.
